    <string name="share_app_text">Do you have issues with SMS being converted to MMS after three pages? With this app, you can send long text messages as SMS without automatic MMS conversion, send to one or multiple recipients, with no limitations on message length and without the common issues caused by carriers or restrictions on some Android devices.\n\nDownload from CafeBazaar:\n%1$s\n\nGitHub:\n%2$s</string>
